<title>Wait for the Lord</title>
<aka>Pan blisko jest</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
.Em         C      Am6    B
 Pan blisko jest, oczekuj Go.
.Em  D      G           Am B  Em
 Pan blisko jest, w Nim serca moc.
 ***
 Wait for the Lord, His day is near.
 Wait for the Lord:
 keep watch, take heart.</lyrics>
